David Jones Limited Appoints International Business Machines Corp As Platform Provider

Thursday, 9 Feb 2012 08:57pm EST

David Jones Limited announced that it has appointed International Business Machines Corp (IBM) as the provider of its new Multi-Channel Retail Systems Platform. Under the terms of its appointment IBM will develop an end-to-end multi-channel e-commerce platform (the IBM Smarter Commerce Solution) for David Jones that will enable it to provide customers with a seamless customer experience across its physical stores, its online stores and mobile devices.Â 

